data.description: 103 Lynn Wood St. Excellent opportunity to have the privacy of living in the country with the convenience to the city. Just a very short drive to downtown Morganton, I-40 and many shopping and dining options with no city taxes! Perfect for the growing family, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is move-in ready! Recent updates! Home also has replacement windows! Relax in the spacious and private backyard and enjoy the in-ground pool! Huge partially finished basement with a woodstove and endless opportunities. This home offers a very private 1+ acre wooded lot. It will not last long! Please schedule to view this home today.
